OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury to meet Pope
OL,4,CLeo amid calls for peace
OL,6,FThe first woman to hold the highest
OL,7,Fministry of the Church of England is
OL,8,Fto meet Pope Leo as both religious
OL,9,Fleaders continued to call for peace
OL,10,Famid ongoing war.
OL,12,FThe Archbishop of Canterbury and the
OL,13,Fleader of the world's Catholics will
OL,14,Fjoin for discussion and prayer at the
OL,15,FVatican on Monday.
OL,17,FDame Sarah Mullally, who is on her
OL,18,Ffirst pilgrimage to Rome since being
OL,19,Fformally enthroned in her new role in
OL,20,FMarch, has described the historic
OL,21,Fevent as a "joy and privilege".
OL,26,@}D@LOU}D@^O]
