OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777255442
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury to meet Pope
OL,4,CLeo amid calls for peace
OL,6,FThe meeting comes at a time when the
OL,7,FPope has faced scathing criticism from
OL,8,FUS President Donald Trump, who earlier
OL,9,Fthis month branded the religious
OL,10,Fleader "weak on crime, and terrible
OL,11,Ffor foreign policy" and demanded he
OL,12,F"focus on being a great Pope, not a
OL,13,Fpolitician".
OL,15,FThe pontiff had used his first Easter
OL,16,Fmessage to strongly criticise war,
OL,17,Fcalling on "those who have weapons
OL,18,F(to) lay them down".
OL,26,@rD@HOUsD@SO]tD@AOUuD@KO]yD@LOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
