OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777255442
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury to meet Pope
OL,4,CLeo amid calls for peace
OL,6,FThe Pope doubled down on his comments
OL,7,Ffollowing Mr Trump's criticism,
OL,8,Fwarning during his recent four-nation
OL,9,FAfrica tour that the world is being
OL,10,F"ravaged by a handful of tyrants".
OL,12,FDame Sarah issued a statement at the
OL,13,Ftime backing the Pope's calls for
OL,14,Fpeace.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
