PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777255442
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury to meet Pope
OL,4,CLeo amid calls for peace
OL,6,FShe said she stood in solidarity with
OL,7,Fthe pontiff "in his courageous call
OL,8,Ffor a kingdom of peace" and urged "all
OL,9,Fthose entrusted with political
OL,10,Fauthority to pursue every possible
OL,11,Fpeaceful and just means of resolving
OL,12,Fconflict".
OL,14,FEchoing this in a sermon in the
OL,15,FItalian capital on Sunday, she said
OL,16,Fthat in the world today instead of
OL,17,Fjustice and peace being prioritised,
OL,18,Fthere is "violence inflicted on
OL,19,Finnocent people in conflicts across
OL,20,Fthe globe".
OL,26,@oD@MOUpD@WO]pD@cOUtD@IO]zD@JOU|D@JO]
