OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777255442
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury to meet Pope
OL,4,CLeo amid calls for peace
OL,6,FAddressing a congregation at the
OL,7,FEpiscopal church of St Paul's Within
OL,8,Fthe Walls ` the first non-Roman
OL,9,FCatholic church to be built within the
OL,10,Fcity's walls ` she also highlighted
OL,11,Fthe importance of speaking up for and
OL,12,Fdefending "the dignity and worth of
OL,13,Fevery human being", including refugees.
OL,15,FThe purpose of her four-day visit is
OL,16,Fsaid by Lambeth Palace to be to
OL,17,F"strengthen Anglican`Roman Catholic
OL,18,Frelations" and "aims to deepen bonds
OL,19,Fof communion, affirm a shared witness,
OL,20,Fand encourage ongoing collaboration at
OL,21,Fboth global and local levels".
OL,26,@tD@KOUuD@RO]yD@AOUzD@JO]zD@POU}D@]O]
