CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777255442
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury to meet Pope
OL,4,CLeo amid calls for peace
OL,6,FShe will meet the Pope on Monday
OL,7,Fmorning for private prayer and
OL,8,Fdiscussion, after which each will give
OL,9,Fan address.
OL,11,FDame Sarah made history when she was
OL,12,Fnamed the first female Archbishop of
OL,13,FCanterbury, and had also served as the
OL,14,Ffirst female Bishop of London.
OL,16,FWhile the Church of England first
OL,17,Fordained women priests in 1994, women
OL,18,Fcannot become priests in the Catholic
OL,19,FChurch.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
