PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777255442
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury to meet Pope
OL,4,CLeo amid calls for peace
OL,6,FAt Dame Sarah's enthronement in
OL,7,FCanterbury last month, a campaigner
OL,8,Fwho said she has been advocating for
OL,9,Fwomen's ordination in the Catholic
OL,10,FChurch for 50 years stood outside the
OL,11,Fcathedral holding a sign saying
OL,12,F"Catholics, let's do this".
OL,14,FJane Varner Malhotra, 57, from
OL,15,FWashington DC, said she hoped the
OL,16,FVatican was "paying attention".
OL,18,FThe archbishop will also join the Pope
OL,19,Ffor midday prayer in the Chapel of
OL,20,FUrban VIII within the Apostolic Palace.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@ZO]xD@MOUxD@^O]
